      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一月三日　昼",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.9333332221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、誕生日だって言ったらメイクさんに髪をセット\nしてもらっちゃった。こういうのも新鮮でいいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5333326499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "けど、さっきの仕事で着た衣装……\nお腹回りがちょっと、いやかなりキツく感じたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1333326657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3333326499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "忘年会や新年会が続いて油断してたわね\nちゃんと自制するようにしなくちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4066.666666599996,
          "startTime": 32.3333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7033.333333299996,
          "startTime": 35.3
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9066.666666599996,
          "startTime": 37.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 31.983332777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "やあ遙子、お疲れ様……へぇ、髪型がいつもと違うね\nうん、良く似合ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、葵ちゃん！　……あら？\nなんだか甘いいい匂いがするわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "誕生パーティー用のお菓子を作っていたからね\nもちろん、料理の準備もばっちりだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、主役の帰りを心待ちにしてる……ん？\n複雑そうな顔をしてるね。何かあった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "（さ、さすが葵ちゃん鋭いわね！）\n（でも、自分から言うのはちょっと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15799.999999999996,
          "startTime": 86.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、あの……みんなの気持ちはすっごく嬉しいのよ？\nでも私、今はあんまりお腹空いてなくて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "きゃっ！？　え、えっと、今の音は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.300003767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "今のってお腹の音だよね？　聞いたところお腹は\n空いてそうだけど……もしかして体調悪いとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "違うの！　そうじゃないのよ！　……じ、実は今日\n収録で着た衣装のことなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.299995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "その、サイズがね？　合わなかったって言うか……\nちょっとだけ窮屈に感じたって言うか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほど、そういうことか\n大きいとそれはそれで苦労するという話は本当なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.400008138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "（お、大きい？　お腹のことかしら？）\n（葵ちゃん、オブラートに包んで話してくれてる？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "でも心配無用だよ、遙子。お菓子を食べたところで\nそれ以上成長することはない。僕が保証するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3804042253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ？　まさか、ドーナツは穴が空いてるから\n実質カロリーゼロみたいな、そんな話本当にあるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツは知らないけど、僕のお菓子は食べても\n平気だよ。僕を見れば分かるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "（確かに葵ちゃんは全然太ってないわね……そうだわ）\n（葵ちゃんはダンサー……ダンサーはスタイルが命！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "（当然、自分が食べるものにも気を遣うはず……）\n（きっとカロリー低めのお菓子を用意してくれたのね！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "何より今日は誕生日なんだし、我慢なんてしたら\nもったいないよ。せっかくみんなで準備したんだしさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうよね。みんなにだって失礼だわ……\n決めた！　今日はチートバースデーよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "お菓子もお料理も浴びるほど食べてやるんだから！\n遙子、一線越えまーす！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "その意気その意気……しかしまだ発育途上とは\nやっぱり面白いな、遙子って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.6000132243,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}